' description: archive_plan tool 4 子模块原子收口 sequence — 4 段 (入口 / 预检 / 收口 / cleanup)
' last_updated: 2026-05-29
@startuml archive-plan-flow

title archive_plan — 4 子模块原子收口 sequence (precheck + ff-merge + archive-fs + cleanup)

actor Caller as C
participant "archive_plan facade" as H
participant "收口业务层\n(impl)" as I
participant "预检助手 + INDEX 同步助手" as PC
participant "数据表 (会话)" as DB
participant "baton 收尾\n(关 teammate + 归档 caller)" as BC
participant "会话管理器" as SM
participant "git + fs" as IO

== 段 1: 入口 + 白名单 + cwd 反查 ==

C -> H: invoke(plan_id, worktree_path, base_branch?, plan_file_path?, changelog_id?)
note right of H
  入口拦截器: 白名单 deny external (写 git + 删 worktree 高风险)
  fail-open: DB throw / row null → 退化 default + warnings.push
end note
H -> DB: 反查 caller cwd + cwdReleaseMarker
DB --> H: { cwd, cwdReleaseMarker }

== 段 2: 进 impl + precheck 8 分支决策 ==

H -> I: archivePlanImpl(args, mergedDeps)
I -> PC: runPrecheck (笛卡尔 cwdValid × inWorktree × markerReal 8 分支短路 + 其他预检)
note right of PC
  8 分支决策 (cwdValid × inWorktree × markerReal):
  ① cwd valid + inWorktree + marker==worktreePath → pass + releaseMarkerOnSuccess (跨 adapter)
  ② cwd valid + inWorktree + marker==null → reject (cwd-resilience guard)
  ③ cwd valid + inWorktree + marker 指其他 worktree → reject (cross-worktree archive 不允许)
  ④ cwd valid + !inWorktree + marker==worktreePath → pass + releaseMarkerOnSuccess
  ⑤ cwd valid + !inWorktree + marker==null → pass (默认 caller 已 ExitWorktree keep)
  ⑥ cwd valid + !inWorktree + marker 指其他 worktree → warn 不释放 marker
  ⑦ cwd invalid + marker==worktreePath → pass + releaseMarkerOnSuccess
  ⑧ cwd invalid + marker 指其他 → reject
end note
PC --> I: precheck OK + releaseMarkerOnSuccess 字段
I -> IO: realpath + plan frontmatter parse (plan_id ↔ worktree_path cross-check)

== 段 3: 4 子模块原子收口 (precheck/ff-merge 前失败可 retry; post-ff-merge 失败 manual recovery 无自动 rollback) ==

I -> IO: runFfMerge Step 7-8c: git checkout base_branch + ff-merge worktree-<plan_id>
note right of IO
  base_branch resolution chain:
  caller args.base_branch > plan frontmatter.base_branch > "main" fallback
  强烈建议 plan frontmatter 显式写 base_branch
  (避免 ff-merge 错合主线污染)
  **失败兜底**: ff-merge 失败 → return error + phaseHint;ff-merge 成功后失败进入 manual recovery
end note
I -> IO: runArchiveFs Step 9: 写 plan frontmatter (status=completed + final_commit + completed_at)
I -> IO: runArchiveFs Step 10: mv plan → ref/plans/<plan_id>.md

opt spike-reports/ 存在 (Step 11)
  I -> IO: runArchiveFs Step 11: mv spike-reports/ → ref/plans/<plan_id>/
  note right of IO
    mv 失败 (EXDEV / perm) → warnings.push hint (不阻塞)
  end note
end

I -> PC: runArchiveFs Step 12: sync INDEX (smart update 4 态)
note right of PC
  4 态: created / appended / updated / unchanged
  RMW 单飞锁防 TOCTOU 并发写丢
end note
PC --> I: plansIndexAction

I -> IO: runArchiveFs Step 12.5: git add + commit (pathspec 隔离 3 critical paths + spike-reports/)
I -> DB: runCleanup Step 13: 清 cwdReleaseMarker (提前到 commit 后\n→ Step 14 失败时 marker 已清,caller 跑别 plan 不撞 stale)
I -> IO: runCleanup Step 14: git worktree remove + branch -D

I --> H: { archivedPath, commitHash, plansIndexAction, warnings, spikeReportsArchived }

== 段 4: baton cleanup phase 1+2 (与 hand_off 共享 helper) ==

H -> BC: runBatonCleanup({callerSid, toolName: 'archive_plan'})
note right of BC
  archive_plan 永远跑 phase 1 (plan 收口 = team 整片收口)
end note

BC -> SM: phase 1: 关 caller 同 team 全部 teammate\n(dedup 跨 team 共享 sid, per-sid try/catch)
SM --> BC: { closed, failed, skipped }

BC -> DB: phase 2: 归档 caller (failed warn-only 不阻塞)
SM --> BC: archived: 'ok' / 'failed' / 'skipped'

BC --> H: { teammatesShutdown, archived }

== 收口 ok return ==

H --> C: ok({ archivedPath, commitHash, branchDeleted, worktreeRemoved,\n  plansIndexAction, warnings, spikeReportsArchived, archived, teammatesShutdown })

@enduml
